{"tid":2259984,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"機箱推薦討論","createTime":"2020-10-27T08:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T06:39:40.000Z","uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e12c277644e1908654d22572b1fe040f5b620d1c","tid":2259984,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:35:13.000Z","msg":"求推薦機箱，要求:<br />\n<br />\n1) 中塔/全塔式， 最少都要啱大嘅matx板。<br />\n2) 預3風扇版本嘅 display card 位<br />\n3) 個樣 &gt;&gt; 散熱 ， 散熱可以自己諗辦法再改，但整容好難。唔使預水冷，散熱會自己之後就個箱嘅深度。<br />\n4) 有側透最好，無都ok 。 一定唔要玻璃板<br />\n5) 唔會特登玩RGB，唔介意機箱有定無燈效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbudget 3千左右， 如果有啱條件嘅1/2百啲蚊雞嘢都唔抗拒。"},{"pid":"454872a0c57b00df879b029e14327be657f6d11f","tid":2259984,"uid":279829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:56:28.000Z","msg":"樓主個筆直係齋箱？<br />\n定計埋其他雜費（水冷等）？"},{"pid":"9e2814e99dba0d67039e5fda2a55e05c402ef6f8","tid":2259984,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"454872a0c57b00df879b029e14327be657f6d11f","tid":2259984,"uid":279829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:56:28.000Z","msg":"樓主個筆直係齋箱？<br />\n定計埋其他雜費（水冷等）？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:59:18.000Z","msg":"齋箱， 但唔介意1/2百蚊嘅雞嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果3千包其他料，個殼應該係全空氣制造<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf9b7386973c4cd01237f1713f94d5648b0abc0","tid":2259984,"uid":279829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:02:06.000Z","msg":"暫時都未買過4位數價位嘅箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n交俾其他高手指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65729b883a964c96d045b3189450309a9b4c03e7","tid":2259984,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acf9b7386973c4cd01237f1713f94d5648b0abc0","tid":2259984,"uid":279829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:02:06.000Z","msg":"暫時都未買過4位數價位嘅箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"